## üöÄ Core Features

### 1. Sorting Algorithm Visualizer
Visualize and compare the most essential sorting algorithms with step-by-step execution:

- **Algorithms Included:**
  - Bubble Sort
  - Quick Sort
  - Merge Sort
  - Insertion Sort
  - Selection Sort

- **Features:**
  - Real-time bar chart animations
  - Comparison and swap counters
  - Adjustable speed control (slow motion to instant)
  - Custom input support
  - Random data generation with variable sizes (5-50 elements)
  - Color-coded states: Comparing (yellow), Swapping (red), Sorted (green)

---

### 2. Searching Algorithm Visualizer
Understand how different search strategies locate target elements:

- **Algorithms Included:**
  - Linear Search
  - Binary Search
  - Jump Search
  - Exponential Search

- **Features:**
  - Visual highlighting of search path
  - Step counter and comparison tracking
  - Custom array input
  - Target value configuration

